description: This file configures a service worker for the Qwik framework, primarily setting up prefetching and lifecycle event handlers.

methods.name: addEventListener
methods.description: Registers event listeners for 'install' and 'activate' lifecycle events in the service worker.

methods.name: self.skipWaiting
methods.description: Advances the service worker to the activate state immediately upon installation.

methods.name: self.clients.claim
methods.description: Claims control of all clients immediately upon activation.
